Author: sublimeAuxiliatrix
Text: After chugging the rest of my water bottle and placing it on the coffee table, my boyfriend just looked at me perplexed and said, “how do you drink so much water every day?!”  I have become a water spirit.  I am made of water now.

Author: sickcupcake
Text: Chugging water until I stop thinking about the bomb ass pasta that’s downstairs. 🙃It’s fine. We’re fine. Water is delicious.
